Aristarchus Grammar:

program = def ... question ...


def = (body Identifier Number Number)
    | (connection Identifier Identifier Identifier Number)
    | (system Identifier [Listof Variable])



question = variable 
         | (lagrange variable)
         | (L1 variable)
         | (L2 variable)
         | (L3 variable)
         | (L4 variable)
         | (L5 variable)
         | (kepler3-period variable)
         | (escape-velocity variable)
         | (surface-gravity variable)

